snippet.description:
Thomas and Friends  Peppa Pig Disney Pixar Cars Play Doh Surprise Eggs Minions Sofia The First  Paw Patrol Disney Mickey Mouse Frozen Mermaids Spongebob and lots more all made in to Family Friendly Fun Videos.

Who are we? We are the Phillips family from the UK, living just outside of London. consisting of Ian & Ali (mum & dad) and our 3 boys, Chris, Dave & Mike. We love making fun and educational videos with toys showing how toys can be mixed together for maximum play value. We're also fascinated by the variety of different surprise eggs you can get and keep inventing different ways that they can be opened. We started YouTube just making toy train videos but have since moved in to all different types of toys. We try and release a new video everyday so if you haven't already subscribed now is a great time to do so. Remember the emphasis is on "Family Friendly" .

snippet.title: Awakening Records
snippet.description:
Awakening Records is the record label for artists, musicians and singers Maher Zain, Mesut Kurtis, Hamza Namira, Raef and Harris J. We started Awakening in the year 2000 as an Islamic publishing house in the UK, and in 2008 we went into music field when Awakening Records produced Al-Mu'allim album 2003 and first music video by Sami Yusuf Al-Mu'allim in September 2004. We went on to produce more songs, albums and music videos that millions around the world enjoy to this day.

Awakening was founded by four young British and American Muslim entrepreneurs. Awakening Worldwide is a media production company with offices around the world, focusing on music production, live events, and book publishing. Awakening is headquartered in London with operational offices in both Egypt and the USA.

Buy our albums & publications from Awakening Store (Worldwide shipping available):
http://www.AwakeningStore.com

For inquiries and booking requests, please email us:
info@awakening.org
